The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Punters Corner - Make My Day has it easy
                                                                                                                       7                                                                                      Make My Day has it easy 
            STAR RACER                            
	Calcutta: The 2-1 favourite, Make My Day scored a handsome victory in Saturdays feature event, the 1,400m Independence Cup. The two and half-a-length victory of the Rashid Byramji-trained filly, over Must Be Magic and Strike A Deal  also three-year-old fillies  came about the time when punters were beginning to lose faith in the present classic crop. Apprentice B. Mahesh, who partnered the filly also rode a well-judged race on the Emerald Cat daughter.           
	The afternoons six-event card, for a change, was ruled by the fancied runners and the favourites.          
	RESULTS          
	1. Best Of The Blues Plate: Avesco (C.Alford) 1, Queen Vic 2, Silken Dancer 3. Won by: 6-3/4, Dist; (1-32.18). Win Rs 17; (P) 13, 13; (Q) 23; Shp: 30; (T) 67. Fav: Avesco.           
	2. Callisto Handicap: Grand Pere (Shailesh) 1, Mrs Jones 2, Bay Magic 3. Won by: 1-3/4, 7; (1-8.1). Win Rs 34; (P) 17, 16, 28; (Q) 61; Shp: 56; (T) 556. Fav: Mrs Jones.           
	3. Tasmac Handicap: Glorious Invention (M.Krishna) 1, Apyrous 2, Manege 3. Won by: 2, 3/4; (1-14.61). Win Rs 19; (P) 12, 61, 47; (Q) 219; Shp: 194; (T) 2,575. Fav: Glorious Invention.           
	4. Independence Cup: Make My Day (B.Mahesh) 1, Must Be Magic (A.Imran) 2, Strike A Deal (C.Alford) 3. Won by: 2-1/2, 2-3/4; (1-32.81). Win Rs 33; (P) 15, 39, 19; (Q) 361; Shp: 96; (T) 1,962. Fav: Make My Day.           
	5. Compassionate Handicap: Auckley (Shezad) 1, Ashridge 2, Temptation 3. NR: Sea Monarch. Won by: 4, 5-1/2, 4; (2-5.78). Win Rs 46; (P) 16, 14, 19; (Q) 41; Shp: 55; (T) 287. Fav: Ashridge.           
	6. Anokato Handicap: Argentina (Pawan) 1, Italian Dream 2, Ocean Dancer 3. Won by: 1-1/2, 2, (1-36.58). Win Rs 31; (P) 15, 26, 45; (Q) 297; Shp: 124; (T) 6,365. Fav: De La Paix.          
	Jackpot: Rs 8,739; (C) Rs 516.          
